{"tid":2230552,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人住要買一個禮拜的食材點做","createTime":"2020-10-05T04:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T05:55:59.000Z","uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9a8b4fece4b50970f27adf5e17a22db608b9b6","tid":2230552,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"宜家通常自己煮<br />\n好少出去食飯<br />\n月頭會去買齊晒啲物資夠一個月用<br />\n通常飲品一入就一箱咖啡一箱beverage <br />\n食材就買足夠食一星期的份量<br />\n主要買凍牛有平有貴、菜就買一包夠我食三日<br />\n仲有其他bacon,luncheon,egg啲雜野<br />\n求教有咩suggestion可以多樣化啲<br />\n預備戒嚴或打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c51595078cf0d66c3e1d08f23873389fcc257ee","tid":2230552,"uid":5793,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"135食午餐肉<br />\n246食五香肉丁<br />\n星期日食豆豉鯪魚"},{"pid":"a0b8277e9728ebcc849cfca00ffb08bd926480be","tid":2230552,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"白米一包"},{"pid":"d1877f6f3d37f656e87a58ce1ac782d84c73d14f","tid":2230552,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"一箱杯麵，收工"},{"pid":"8ba04be8856e6bab0208c3ddd0c5f3561ea402ca","tid":2230552,"uid":53592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"雞胸、三文魚、菜"},{"pid":"145784e7bbc8db0b54e1397ee128484caa90c8fb","tid":2230552,"uid":260581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T05:55:59.000Z","msg":"買完返黎 搵保鮮紙包好<br />\n放入freezer 咁d肉類可以放幾個月<br />\n到你想食既時候再拎出黎融雪<br />\n咁你買到返黎 咪唔一定一個星期內食曬<br />\n仲可以慢慢諗點煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}